    <name>UDL Goal-Setting Guidelines for instructional design​</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{92844aa9-8bbe-4831-8786-644c3a39d251}{206}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Read the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.cast.org/binaries/content/assets/common/publications/downloads/cast-udltipsfordevelopinglearninggoals-20200920-a11y.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;10 tips for UDL goals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;. Select one tip and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;start using it in your teaching practice. Consider re-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;designing a lesson or a learning space. Point out your&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;change to your learners and tell them why you&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;selected that specific tip.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Start with a clear goal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Share goals in multiple ways.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Frame goals with expert learning in mind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Separate the goal from the means.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{92844aa9-8bbe-4831-8786-644c3a39d251}{221}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:540,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-540,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}" data-indent="-540" style="font-size: 1.7rem; display: inline !important;"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@424242,9," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Prepare your assessment with the goals in mind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Include opportunities for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;personal connections to goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Divide large goals into sub-goals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;or objectives (create pathways).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Consider the process as well as&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;the final product.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Provide models and examples.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Offer authentic opportunities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;for assessment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Go back to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="$@COURSEVIEWBYID*290@$#section-5" target="_blank" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;Try It Yourself Section&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a list of all Try it Yourself Options.​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{92844aa9-8bbe-4831-8786-644c3a39d251}{227}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:10,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-contrast="auto" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider%20wave.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
